data.description: Newly renovated Mediterranean style home nestled in the highly sought-out area within San Antonio's Northside. Featuring an entry hall that gives way to the formal dining space leading to a chefs kitchen and living space. Backyard has artificial turf for year round enjoyment. Just minutes away from hiking and biking trails at Eisenhower park. Newly renovated community center and pool area with quick city highway access to 281, 1604 & I-10.
